<!--
====================================================
HTML PROJECT THINKING CHECKLIST (START HERE)
====================================================

1== WHAT IS THIS PAGE DOING?

Ask BEFORE writing any HTML:

- Is the user just READING content?
- Is the user ENTERING information?
- Is this STRUCTURED data (rows / columns)?
- Is this a LIST of related items?
- Is this mainly PAGE LAYOUT?

This determines the main container element.


2== CHOOSE THE MAIN CONTAINER


USER ENTERS DATA  → <form>
- inputs, checkboxes, radios, dropdowns, textarea
- requires labels and a submit button

STRUCTURED DATA → <table>
- rows + columns
- schedules, comparisons

LIST OF ITEMS → <ul> or <ol>
- bullet points
- steps
- options

PAGE STRUCTURE / CONTENT → semantic layout
- <header>
- <main>
- <section>
- <footer>


3== IF THIS IS A FORM, CONFIRM ALL OF THESE


FORM BASICS:
- <form> element exists
- Every input has a <label>
- label "for" matches input "id"
- Required fields use "required"

COMMON INPUT PATTERNS:

TEXT:
<label for="name"></label>
<input id="name" type="text" placeholder="" required>

EMAIL (HTML5 validation):
<input id="email" type="email" required>

NUMBER (range validation):
<input id="number" type="number" min="" max="">

RADIO (one choice only):
- Same name attribute
<input type="radio" name="group" value="">

CHECKBOX (multiple choices):
- Each has a value
<input type="checkbox" value="">

DROPDOWN:
<select id="dropdown">
  <option value=""></option>
</select>

TEXTAREA:
<textarea rows="" cols=""></textarea>

SUBMIT BUTTON:
<button id="submit" type="submit">Submit</button>


4== ATTRIBUTE SANITY CHECK

- id values are UNIQUE
- label for="" matches input id=""
- Valid input types only (text, email, number, etc.)
- min / max → numbers only
- minlength / maxlength → text only
- value → radios, checkboxes, buttons

------------------------------------
5== FINAL SELF-CHECK
------------------------------------

Ask:
"If I came back in 3 months, would this make sense?"

If no:
- Add comments
- Rename things clearly
- Simplify structure

====================================================
END CHECKLIST
====================================================
-->
